<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000025/2025-26/syllabus/0> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 0 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "1. Fundamentals of Academic Writing. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000025/2025-26/syllabus/1> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 1 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "2. The grammar of academic discourse. Distinguishing between academic and personal styles. Connecting events in a text. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000025/2025-26/syllabus/2> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 2 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "3. Creating the whole text: the language of coherence and connection; use of hedges, and boosters. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000025/2025-26/syllabus/3> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 3 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "4. The structure of the abstract or proposal. Tema 3. The role of terminology in specialized languages. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000025/2025-26/syllabus/4> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 4 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "5. Specialized vocabulary and formal academic vocabulary. The language to contrast, define, summarize or emphasize. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000025/2025-26/syllabus/5> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 5 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "6. Oral & Listening skills. English as a Lingua Franca. Interaction with students in English. Issues in understanding spoken English Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000025/2025-26/syllabus/6> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 6 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "7. Attending lectures. Signposting and identifying key points in a lecture, note-taking. Paraphrasing and summarizing. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000025/2025-26/syllabus/7> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 7 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "8. Syllabus development. Trends in the teaching of a foreign language. English as a Medium of Instruction versus CLIL Strategies. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000025/2025-26/syllabus/8> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 8 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "9. Preparing for interactive lecturing. Structure of the oral presentation. Organizing content. Body language and delivery. Preparing the unit/lesson plan Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000025/2025-26/syllabus/9> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 9 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "10. Microteaching sessions. Sin subniveles"@es .

